=== ELEMENTAL DYNAMICS ===

Meta (вҲ®) at 0.75: ReverseвҖ”the meta-operation. Flipping the bow-tie,
harmonic collapse, making output input. The pattern that patterns
itself.

Wood (ОІ) at 0.70: ModifyвҖ”generative range. Magnify/minify, volumetric
change, expansion and contraction of the field.

Air (Пғ) at 0.70: SubstituteвҖ”distinction-making. The cut that replaces,
reclassification, what signal replaces what noise.

Water (ПҒ) at 0.65: CombineвҖ”relational resonance. Merging streams,
